--> Comparison
		than			yerine
		rather than		yerine
		whether or not		olsun ya da olmasın
		as much as		olduğu kadar
		whereas			oysa
									it is said that hunger develops intelligence, whereas satiety, on the contrary, dulls it
										açlığın zekâyı geliştirdiği, oysa tokluğun ise tam tersine körelttiği söylenir
		similarly		benzer şekilde			My friend works every day of the week, similarly, I work a lot too
									Husband and wife were similarly successful in their careers
		equally			eşit olarak
		likewise		aynı şekilde			The food was excellent likewise the wine
									Her second marriage was likewise unhappy
									My friends were happy and likewise I was happy too
		just as			tıpkı, -dığın gibi		She got mad just as I expected
									The house was just as she had imagined
		just like		tıpkı	
		similar to		-a benzer
		same as			aynı
		by the same token	aynı şekilde
		in like manner		benzer şekilde
		like			benzer
		another ... like	bir diğer .. gibi
		in the same way		aynı şekilde,			I'm obsessed with Asian food, in the same way, my cousin likes it too
					-dığın gibi, -dığın şekilde	You must exercise your mind every day, in the same way that you exercise your body
									You can eat kimbab in the same way that you eat sushi
		as with			olduğu gibi
		comparable		karşılaştırılabilir 


