# Addition Conjunctions
	and		ve			I have two cases and a bag with me
						you can pack your things and you can leave
	also		aynı zamanda		they paid for  dinner at the restaurant, also, they paid for the taxi	
						there is also a bakery in the neighbourhood
						we also joined team
	not only ... but also	sadece .. değil, aynı zamanda			
						to accomplish great things, we must not only dream, but also act
						not only plan, but also believe
						he not only studies hard, but also works well
	in addition	ek olarak (daha resmi)
	additionally				our new director can speak three languages, in addition, he has six years of experience
						our new house is so close to the city center, additionally, it has four large bedrooms
	in addition to	ek olarak		in addition to my weekly wage, I have got a lot of tips
	moreover 	dahası (daha resmi)
	furthermore	dahası			the whole report is badly written, moreover, it is inaccurate
						I don't want to go there furthermore, I have no time to do so
						he is lazy, and furthermore, he has no sense of responsibility	- sorumluluk bilinci
	besides		dahası, ayrıca, yanında	I don't want to go, besides, I'm too tired
						besides working as a doctor, he also writes novels in his spare time
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 
# Replacement Conjunctions
	or		ya da			you can join me, or, you can stay at home
	or else		yoksa			hurry up, or else, you will be late
						the book must be here, or else, you have lost it
						they can't be coming, or else, they would have called
						you had better hand over the money, or else.
	alternatively	alternatif olarak	we could take the train or, alternatively, go by car
						we could go to the Indian restaurant or, alternatively, we could try the new Italian place
