		BECAUSE
			as a result of - nın sonucu olarak
			as things go - bu şekilde geliştiğinden
			considering - göz önüne alarak
			due to - sebebiyle
			by virtue of - sayesinde
			for the sake of - bu uğurda
			in view of - bu bakış açısı ile
			on grounds that - gerekçesiyle
			whereas - buna karşılık

		



		
--> Explaining
	as, since, in so far as, because, the reason why
		- as she left the kitchen, her daughter followed her
		- it has helped seen substantial creations in so far as game quality and design
			Oyun kalitesi ve tasarımı açısından önemli kreasyonların görülmesine yardımcı oldu
		- since the restaurant is located at a beach resort, it is a good choice for hungry people who have just finished exploring the beach
			Restoran bir sahil beldesinde bulunduğundan, sahili keşfetmeyi yeni bitirmiş aç insanlar için iyi bir seçimdir
		- I love to go to the cafe, because I like to see my friends
			arkadaşlarımı görmeyi sevdiğimden, o kafeye gitmeyi seviyorum
		- we have to understand the reason why we do these certain ceremonies in life
			hayatta bu belli törenleri neden yaptığımızı anlamalıyız
		
--> Choice
	or, whatever, whoever, neither ... nor, either ... or
		- I don't know how many times or how many ways I can say I'm sorry
			bilmiyorum kaç kere ya da kaç şekilde özür dilerim diyebileceğimi
		- whatever technique is employed, an electric generator is required
			hangi teknik kullanılırsa kullanılsın, bir elektrik jeneratörü gereklidir
		- she evidently saw this thief, whoever he may have been
			her kimse bu hırsız, belli ki o hırsızı görmüş
		
		
--> Manner
	how, as though, as if
		- he behaved as if nothing had happened			hiçbir şey olmamış gibi davrandı
	
--> Generalisation
	as a rule, for the most part, in general, generally, on the whole, overall, in most cases

--> Place
	where, wherever, here, there, in the back, adjacent to, next to, nearby, beyond, opposite to, at the point

--> Adverb clauses of Place
	where, wherever, everywhere, anywhere
	
--> relative pronouns
	who, whoever, whom, whomever, whose

--> relative adjectives
	that, whatever, which, whichever





due to, owing to, on account of, because of, in view of, by virtue of, as a result of		... den dolayı, ... yüzünden, ... sonucunda
despite, inspite of, for all, notwithstanding							... e rağmen
as well as, in addition to, besides, along with, coupled with, together with			... nın yanı sıra, ... ile birlikte
in contrast to, as opposed to, contrary to, unlike						... nın aksine
however, but, yet, nonetheless, nevertheless, even so, still					fakat, yine de
because, as, since, now that, in that, given that, seeing that, knowing that, for		... dığı için, çünkü
therefore, so, thus, thereby, hence, that’s why, as a result, as a consequence, accordingly	bu yüzden, dolayısıyla
moreover, furthermore, what is more, besides, in addition, additionally, also			dahası, ek olarak
in order to, so as to, with a view to, in an attempt to, in a bid to, with the intention of 	... niyetiyle, ... mek için


	

